<p>
Chain Drive is an action mini-game which condenses all the piloting and fighting gameplay from Kromaia in a vintage arcade style experience. Now the only goal is to survive in order to face a bigger swarm, achieve a longer combo, fight a harder boss and get to the Olympus of High Scores. <b>You gain access to our current  version of this mini-game and the final DRM-Free digital version on release</b>.</p>
<p><b>+ [Current version: PC-Windows. Take a look at our Stretch Goals for Linux and Mac support]<br></b></p>
