<p><a href="http://www.krakenempire.com/kromaia/igg/Kromaia_Tau_02_LARGE.jpg" target="_blank" rel="nofollow"><img style="max-width:580px;" src="http://images.indiegogo.com/file_attachments/89171/files/20130922092915-Kromaia_Tau_02.jpg?1379867355"></a></p>As we said, the way to reach this point has not been easy at all. In addtition to the years of self-funding, we have had to push our engine to the limit to overcome some limitations and being able to achieve the features and performance we wanted. Now we can say we are convinced that Kromaia will be a truly unique experience and determined to give our best to complete a great game.<br><br>With all that work and time spent in a project, having your game more exposed to the public before it's finished is not a decision to be taken lightly, even more considering Kromaia is far from being a casual game. At its current status, the project needs to gather the support to start the race to the final release more safely, with a strong community, and then evolve according to this support to reach  the quality levels which allow the game to make its way.<br><br>Your help will mean a boost for our team to keep moving forward to materialize such a final effort, deal with licensing, having by our side great professionals and all the costs this final stage implies for our little company. All this will make possible to provide Kromaia with the production values in terms of engineering, art, and music to make a difference.<br><br>Rest assured that we will work harder than ever, and with your support Kromaia will be much more than what we dreamed of.



















